#####Viewing Comments

By default, if you do not include the start and start_id parameters, the GET calls will return the most recent 25 comments on the specified task, Chat view, or List.

To retrieve older comments:

Locate the last (oldest) comment in the response body and add the following values to the parameters of your next call:

- Add the date value to the start parameter

- Add the comment id value to the start_id parameter

Both parameters are required to retrieve the next 25 comments. Repeat as needed to page through all task comments.

When you've reached the final page of comments, you'll either have less than 25 comments in the response, or when you send the next call with the start and start_id parameters, you'll receieve the following response:

```json
{
"comments": []
}
```

